---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import profilePicture from "../assets/profile-picture.jpg";
---

<div id="container">
  <section
    class="relative py-8 sm:py-12 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800"
    aria-label="Introduction"
  >
    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 justify-center lg:justify-items-end py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-24 mx-0 sm:mx-4 lg:mx-8"
    >
      <div
        class="order-2 lg:order-1 p-2 sm:p-4 justify-self-center lg:justify-self-end space-y-6"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h1
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl dark:text-gray-200 leading-normal"
          >
            Hey, I&apos;m{" "}
            <span class="text-(--theme-5) font-bold">Josh</span> ðŸ‘‹
          </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-4">
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            I&apos;m passionate about building robust and scalable software,
            particularly with <strong>TypeScript</strong>, <strong>Go</strong>,
            and <strong>Python</strong>. My background in enterprise SaaS
            informs my approach to crafting solutions, whether it&apos;s
            developing AI-powered platforms or award-winning hackathon projects.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            I&apos;m a Full Stack Engineer at <a
              href="https://www.letsdothis.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-(--theme-5) hover:underline font-semibold"
              >Let&apos;s Do This</a
            >, where I build event discovery and booking platforms that help
            people find events and races worldwide. We handle some of the
            biggest events in the world, including the London Marathon ballot
            system. Day-to-day I work with <strong>TypeScript</strong>, <strong
              >React</strong
            >, and <strong>Node.js</strong> on systems that process hundreds of thousands
            of registrations.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Currently diving deep into the AI landscape - building agents,
            experimenting with LLMs, and exploring the philosophical challenges
            of keeping AI systems creative as they become more intelligent. I
            write about the interesting problems I encounter on my <a
              href="/blog"
              class="text-(--theme-5) hover:underline">blog</a
            >.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Before getting into engineering, I spent 10 years in fintech leading
            enterprise sales to hedge funds and asset managers - the kind of
            clients where your software either works perfectly or you don&apos;t
            get paid. That background means I think about what users actually
            need, not just what&apos;s technically interesting.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 pt-4">
            <a
              href="#projects"
              class="flex-1 sm:flex-none inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium text-white bg-[var(--theme-5)] rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
            >
              Projects
            </a>
            <a
              href="/blog"
              class="flex-1 sm:flex-none inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium text-white bg-[var(--theme-5)] rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
            >
              Blog
            </a>
            <a
              href="#contact"
              class="flex-1 sm:flex-none inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium text-white bg-[var(--theme-5)] rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
            >
              Contact
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 flex justify-center">
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 flex justify-center">
          <Image
            src={profilePicture}
            alt="Josh Tuddenham"
            width={400}
            height={400}
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            class="w-48 h-48 sm:w-64 sm:h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 lg:w-[400px] lg:h-[400px] rounded-full border-4 border-[var(--theme-5)] cursor-pointer dark:brightness-90"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</div>
